# Fluff Date: 2026-03-12 17:26:07
<overview>
<p>The small, steam-powered riverboat described here is not a military craft per se, but an example of an ultra low-tech vehicle that occasionally appears on many worlds either as a tour boat, light transport, or pleasure craft. Suitable for shallow waters, steamers have been pressed into military use over the centuries, often by scouts to covertly transport infantry troops and light gear through hostile waterways.</p>
</overview>

